203
crazy bubble
I was sitting in my room, blowing bubbles and watching them float around the room. I was feeling a bit crazy, so I decided to start popping them with my fingers. Suddenly, one of the bubbles popped and released a cloud of pink smoke. I started coughing and my eyes started watering. I ran to the window and opened it, but the smoke followed me. I started to feel dizzy and lightheaded, so I laid down on the floor. The last thing I remember before I passed out was the sound of the bubble machine going crazy.
